# .helmignore
#
# Patterns to ignore when packaging the chart with `helm package`.
# Works like .gitignore — prevents these files from being included
# in the .tgz artifact when the chart is distributed via a chart repository.

# Documentation files (not needed at runtime)
*.md
environments.md
helm-demo.md

# Editor and OS artifacts
.DS_Store
.vscode/
*.swp
*.bak

# Test fixtures
tests/

# CI/CD local configs
*.local.yaml
